Package common.worker

Class ChangeRequest

java.lang.Object
common.worker.ChangeRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ChangeRequest extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a change request for a park's operational parameters such as capacity, gap between visits, and stay time. This class is used to manage changes and approvals related to park operations.

    • ChangeRequest

      public ChangeRequest(Integer id, String parkName, Integer parkNumber, Integer capacity, Integer gap, Integer staytime, String approved)
      Constructs a new ChangeRequest with specified details.
      Parameters:
      id - Unique identifier for the change request.
      parkName - Name of the park.
      parkNumber - Numerical identifier for the park.
      capacity - Proposed new capacity for the park.
      gap - Proposed new gap between visits.
      staytime - Proposed new stay time for visitors.
      approved - Initial approval status as a string.
